            </div><blockquote>
  <p>&ldquo;Backfire&rdquo; was a submission for <a href="https://itch.io/jam/gmtk-2025" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GMTK Game Jam 2025</a>.</p>

</blockquote><h2 id="overview" class="headerLink">
    <a href="#overview" class="header-mark"></a>Overview</h2><p><strong>A chaotic arcade survival game where every shot might come back to haunt you.</strong></p>
<p>Pilot a nimble tank across a wide-open battlefield. Your mission: stay tethered to the rune stone to charge it to full power. But there’s a twist — every projectile you fire will loop back as a ghost shot… and it’s just as dangerous to you as it is to your enemies.</p>]]></description>
